{"id":266370,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-洞兴高速公路恶意拖欠农民工资百万元/","date":"2012-12-02T14:15:58Z","modified":"2012-12-02T14:15:58Z","title":"维权网 | 洞兴高速公路恶意拖欠农民工资百万元","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员召天明报道）湖南省永州市宁远县天堂镇寡婆桥村农民工陈云胜、欧雪平、朱雄军、何中才、周来宾、邓三宝、何军生、马好生、马成平、周四珍等人反映，他们被湖南洞兴高速公路恶意拖欠血汗钱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈云胜等人说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>，他们与洞新高速湖南段的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>合同段魏农田签订了犬木塘大桥钻孔灌桩协议，当月底有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>多名工人进场开工，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月完工。在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>结账后工程方还欠工人工资共计</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1183973</span><span>元，他们一批工人多次讨要工资未果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>农民工说，后来他们找当地政府和法院，但政府和法院与工程指挥部门一起欺骗农民，至今他们的工资没有着落。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>最后这些农民工希望，政府的职能部门督促施工方尽快结清大家的工资，依法维护农民工的合法权益。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7623029702460911710?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style